{"tid":1260894,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"示威者自發指揮交通疏導車流 過百警察置身事外","createTime":"2019-06-27T03:53:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T04:32:27.000Z","uid":1065,"like":55,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"3aa499bb0991d98fd5a19998f7b189b1d08b69b8","tid":1260894,"uid":1065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T03:53:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/200976479994868/posts/2334950496597445?s=1365081068&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2F200976479994868%2Fposts%2F2334950496597445%3Fs%3D1365081068%26sfns%3Dmo&d=7GYMv7TAV12u%2FDK%2BXNcYJWCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=822f9a7c\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/200976479994868/posts/2334950496597445?s=1365081068&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n黃之鋒 Joshua Wong 在律政中心 Justice Place 。<br />\n<br />\n【黑警不合作運動 2.0】<br />\n由於示威人數眾多，花園道局部變成單線雙程行車，交通一度出現擠塞情況，好彩有多位示威者自發做交通指揮，疏導擠塞，而在場過百警力就匿係暗角蛇王！🐍👮🏻&zwj;♂️<br />\n<br />\n你有糧出都要做埋你嗰份？！🤬🤬🤬🤬<br />\n<br />\n#公僕罷工 #香港人公民質素<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PPK7jwa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPPK7jwa.jpg&h=75d99fd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以話香港警察主要用途係用嚟打壓抗爭者<br />\n根本唔係為咗服務市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab0ab0a14a664e62200462b5b225c1ff7b2ac1a2","tid":1260894,"uid":110332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T03:54:46.000Z","msg":"次次都係我地疏導"},{"pid":"9d7ef0b21f60f7d4459ad394479e087d712aab64","tid":1260894,"uid":32066,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T04:03:46.000Z","msg":"憑咩收30000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5825b5935a8d456a318b8e494b07bb4295a60cdf","tid":1260894,"uid":95520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T04:05:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3b9bd2a6f92d68bb1140501325c5f6c76f50fea2","tid":1260894,"uid":9049,"like":0,"disl